{"tid":256922,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺去台灣旅行當自己出左國玩既人好悲哀","createTime":"2017-05-25T00:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T08:33:02.000Z","uid":68626,"like":23,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b077055652621929177dd3341aa1babea086e325","tid":256922,"uid":68626,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:18:07.000Z","msg":"屌奶星<br />\n去埋晒d up dup 窮撚地方<br />\n繁體字大陸 番大陸就番大陸啦 去乜鳩旅行呀<br />\n唔通我平時番深圳骨場又話自己去撚左旅行？<br />\n仲有班on9仔<br />\n去撚埋晒d乜柒墾丁 話咩餵羊 親親大自然<br />\n依加就黎重陽節 平時山又唔撚見你拜<br />\n去台灣就親親大自然 無撚野呀？<br />\n新界大撚把牛又唔見你同佢玩？<br />\n去台灣玩扮旅行仲要up相上ig個班<br />\n同清明番鄉下拜山up上ig話自己去旅行無分別<br />\n真係人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e0d9093279fb5bd4bf7cc61d0585356f528b37","tid":256922,"uid":46048,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:27:51.000Z","msg":"你都係想提返人就嚟重陽要去拜你姐"},{"pid":"72057e84c2e0fd6cd10c9fb34467d3c209389ece","tid":256922,"uid":68626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都係想提返人就嚟重陽要去拜你姐</blockquote><br />\n你去開台灣！"},{"pid":"fb0f361bbe8c3ff813d8829838b9c1192aa5d3ef","tid":256922,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你都係想提返人就嚟重陽要去拜你姐</blockquote><br />\n你去開台灣？？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4fb94ed5d5363d31ee25b865f3f1286ed7c63a05","tid":256922,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:39:44.000Z","msg":"啱呀 我去台灣當去後花園<br />\n連同班朋友講去台灣都廢事"},{"pid":"c3ec417bf378f4bf8bb7a47a863ba4a344355d4b","tid":256922,"uid":46048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你都係想提返人就嚟重陽要去拜你姐</blockquote><br />\n你去開台灣？？</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n少去"},{"pid":"4c26c3082bf59f178739d3c66416a0f5a2c02726","tid":256922,"uid":106817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T01:03:33.000Z",